{"title":"访醉翁亭","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":5,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访醉翁亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是数不清的摩崖石刻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是看不尽的“墨客”题吟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉翁亭呵醉翁亭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见到的只是高山秀岭、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林木青青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听到的只是莺啼鸟鸣、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水淙淙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但却没有一个人告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那位风流太守——欧阳修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饮酒既然不多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么竟然会醉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的年还未迈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又为什么要称翁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍是浴着潇潇细雨的醉翁亭……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}